{"id": 2244, "genre": 1001, "title": "日常社交中，你都碰到过哪些看起来挺 nice 但有点接受不了的操作？", "description": "一些也许是挺想和你做朋友，但八成做不了朋友的举动。（题图来自：iStock）", "record_count": 4000, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180326161415RNlYctpseOaLx3W8.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-27T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 273152, "content": "刚认识就表现的异常殷勤！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603500}, {"id": 273156, "content": "\n挽手走路", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707201}, {"id": 283909, "content": "不能忍受向陌生人要联系方式，感觉好直接挺尴尬的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003171}, {"id": 273415, "content": "高大尚的企业，招了一批有关系的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299008}, {"id": 274954, "content": "“我这人你就是心直口快”，“我就是这种暴脾气”————既然知道就离我远点儿……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026473}, {"id": 273164, "content": "充大姐，给别人做人生导师", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 740071}, {"id": 273181, "content": "热络的约下次见面", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249991}, {"id": 273443, "content": "大家都是朋友有话好说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290419}, {"id": 273192, "content": "有时间请你吃饭(怎么会请你吃饭?)\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297627}, {"id": 273966, "content": "道德绑架", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234372}, {"id": 276529, "content": "一直在讲自己的“丰富”经历而不会揣测别人心里请你闭嘴的呼喊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622247}, {"id": 272947, "content": "有对象了吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 119, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 49476}, {"id": 275251, "content": "My god ", "image": "img/option/option/20180412002715QtzpsrXamucbTg4G.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839135}, {"id": 272948, "content": "说着话貌似很熟，说完就散了", "image": null, "praise_count": 242, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297047}, {"id": 272949, "content": "要吃饼干吗（还没说完就用手抓着饼干送到了你的嘴边）", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 326299}, {"id": 272950, "content": "加个微信吧 以后方便联系", "image": null, "praise_count": 503, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720773}, {"id": 272951, "content": "自来熟，人家心里还没认可你是他朋友，就开始吧啦吧啦的对人家提一些“我以为的”你应该怎样怎样更好", "image": null, "praise_count": 81, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980926}, {"id": 272953, "content": "一起走吧。但我只想一个人自在地走一路。", "image": null, "praise_count": 189, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285511}, {"id": 273209, "content": "有对象没？然后知道我没有还不给介绍的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298113}, {"id": 272954, "content": "哇你单身？我给你个微信 ta超棒 你们一定很般配（我...我单身主义 靴靴）", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284705}, {"id": 273210, "content": "有对象没？然后知道我没有还不给介绍的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298113}, {"id": 272955, "content": "明明不熟却表现得很熟\n也许是想避免尴尬\n但实际上更尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800043}, {"id": 273723, "content": "非常喜欢干涉别人对于人生的选择和生活方式。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1300535}, {"id": 275515, "content": "还不是很熟，就跟我讲她和男朋友的第一次。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1313188}, {"id": 272956, "content": "好朋友和他姐来家里做客，说到我谈恋爱了，然后他姐直接推荐避孕套品牌", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158677}, {"id": 272957, "content": "敬酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 487, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596413}, {"id": 272958, "content": "现在碰到一般不联系的朋友突然联系你，不是要借钱，那就是要结婚了，23333", "image": null, "praise_count": 157, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1293945}, {"id": 272960, "content": "说是朋友，但是遇到对方说到自己不喜欢的话就开始破口大骂，一副你触到我底线你就该被我骂的态度", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 782673}, {"id": 272961, "content": "太有目的性的搭讪", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 764925}, {"id": 272962, "content": "不对的氛围说这不对的话...尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297080}, {"id": 272963, "content": "对别人得生活充满期盼性  我怎样关你什么事？", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114275}, {"id": 272966, "content": "那些别人好意认识你、自己一副自以为是的样子。才是傻哔", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871583}, {"id": 272967, "content": "给我夹菜", "image": null, "praise_count": 125, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297107}, {"id": 272969, "content": "你往哪边走？\n我想去拉屎，不想告诉你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278143}, {"id": 272970, "content": "我想睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297109}, {"id": 272971, "content": "微信上明明不熟甚至完全不知道怎么加的人的疯狂点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 884747}, {"id": 272972, "content": "全程尬聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297125}, {"id": 272974, "content": "领导说“今天都必须转发朋友圈！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 91, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009817}, {"id": 272976, "content": "说是还是好朋友，确没事不再联系……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1295921}, {"id": 274513, "content": "为了维系她与别人的关系而未事先询问过我的意见就把我的微信给了别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305613}, {"id": 272979, "content": "通过好友空间来加我的说是扩列", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290234}, {"id": 273235, "content": "跟别人一起吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185067}, {"id": 272980, "content": "明明才比自己小一两岁 就一定要叫自己xx姐之类的 女生真的不太喜欢被同龄人喊姐啊 哪怕知道你是客气有礼貌", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918581}, {"id": 272981, "content": "介绍对象！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291284}, {"id": 272982, "content": "未接到邀请的上门——有时候朋友突兀的上门会让我觉得很为难，有时候时间上不方便，有时候是根本就不想让他上门", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 941906}, {"id": 272983, "content": "随便给你贴标签——你是吃货耶！原来你是文艺青年！你很喜欢可爱的东西呢！我觉得你是个很单纯的人！bla bla bla...", "image": null, "praise_count": 116, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023476}, {"id": 272984, "content": "笑点低的人跟你开笑点低的玩笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023476}, {"id": 272985, "content": "我相信你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1296221}, {"id": 272986, "content": "新朋友认为我是很文艺的人，在我朋友圈评论在我看来很装模作样的“文艺”句子", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023476}, {"id": 272987, "content": "看了这么多人的评论，终于知道为什么现在人和人之间这么冷漠了。（因为做什么都总会有人挑剔）", "image": null, "praise_count": 375, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297172}]}